# Codex Reflector Usage

When editing code in this repository:

1. Prefer normal project workflows; codex-reflector runs through hooks and provides second-model feedback.
2. Treat FAIL findings from the reflector as required follow-up work before considering a task complete.
3. Keep verdict lines at the top of reviewer outputs (`PASS` or `FAIL`) to preserve parser reliability.
